    "default_locale": "en-US",
    "description": {
        "en-US": "In Thunderbird, it is currently not possible to delete or detach the attachments of S/MIME signed messages. This annoyed me because I wanted to delete large attachments so that my mailbox would not get too large.\n\nThis addon allows you to disable the S/MIME signature of messages. Afterwards, these messages are no longer recognized as signed and their attachments can be deleted or detached.\n\n<strong>Attention: This addon does not work for encrypted messaged! They must be decrypted first!</strong>"
    },
